  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Accommodation Summary</strong></p>
<p>Chalet Secret de Neige sleeps 14 people and has six spacious bedrooms and six modern bath/shower rooms. This chalet also provides access to a well-equipped kitchen, dining area, living room with fireplace, dressing room and sun terrace.</p>
<p><strong>Ground Floor</strong></p>
<p>Chalet Entrance</p>
<p>Ski boot room and sauna</p>
<p><strong>Room 1 </strong>for two people with two double beds, shower and WC.</p>
<p><strong>Room 2 </strong>for two people with twin beds, shower and WC. The WC is private and off the corridor so not ensuite</p>
<p><strong>First Floor</strong></p>
<p>Lounge and dining area with access to south-facing balcony</p>
<p><strong>Room 3</strong> for two people with a double bed, shower and WC.</p>
<p><strong>Second Floor</strong></p>
<p><strong>Room 4 </strong>for two people with twin beds, shower and WC.</p>
<p><strong>Room 5 </strong>for two or three people with double or twin beds and a single bed. The shower room and WC is private off the corridor (not ensuite) </p>
<p><strong>Room 6</strong> for two or three people with double or twin beds, a single bed, shower and WC</p>
<p>Rooms 5 and 6 have a south facing view and the double/twin beds can be made up as you wish so please let us know if you have a preference at time of booking. </p>
<p><strong>All Inghams chalets have free Wi-Fi.</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
